'''Adolf Hitler''' (ilul di [[20 ibrir]] [[1889]] deg [[Braunau am Inn]], g tmurt n [[Tutrict]] – yemmut di [[30 yebrir]] [[1945]] deg [[Berlin]]) yella d amdan asertay almani, aselway n [[Lalman]] umbeɛd ''[[Führer]]''. Yeḥkem s ukabar i t-ixelqen deg [[1921]], d [[NSDAP]] (''Nationalsozialistische Deutsche Arbeiterpartei''), yexleq daɣen [[Reich wis III]] u ilmend-is tebda [[Imenɣi amaḍlan wis II]]. Sɣur-es id yexleq daɣ isem n [[Tanazit|tnazit]].

== Mai Igu ==
Adolf Hitler Iɣra di Tutrict, tigu tmura wahdes, bauɛdin iflu an Almania, dihi igu lhezb 
n Afellah Almani, badin semminas, Nazi, di 1933 irahhu agellid n Almania. Irro tmurawin tielli xwanten sis Lholafa di Inuɣi Tamzwarit (1914-1918), iosed a-iaɣ Danzeg, d nitet tmura tillellit
tella af ilel n Polanda, Hitler yahjem af polanda di 5:45, di cotenber 1939, s ass-nnes tebda inuɣi.

